indexes.index_definition: CREATE UNIQUE INDEX contract_invoices_pkey ON public.contract_invoices USING btree (id)
CREATE INDEX idx_contract_invoices_contract_id ON public.contract_invoices USING btree (contract_id)
CREATE INDEX idx_contract_invoices_date ON public.contract_invoices USING btree (invoice_date)
CREATE INDEX idx_contract_invoices_holding_id ON public.contract_invoices USING btree (holding_id)
CREATE INDEX idx_contract_invoices_status ON public.contract_invoices USING btree (status)

policies.policyname: Users can delete contract invoices from their holding
policies.qual:
(contract_id IN ( SELECT c.id
   FROM ((contracts c
     JOIN companies comp ON ((c.company_id = comp.id)))
     JOIN user_holdings uh ON ((comp.holding_id = uh.holding_id)))
  WHERE (uh.user_id = auth.uid())))

policies.policyname: Users can insert contract invoices for their holding
policies.with_check:
